# @VERSION spec:gdla v:0.1.0 generated:2026-03-24 source:api-agent
# Project Atlas — Atlas Finance API v2 (target)

@D atlas-finance-api|Atlas finance API for the modernised platform|2.0.0|https://api.acme.internal/finance/v2

@AUTH bearer|JWT bearer issued by Acme SSO|Authorization
@AUTH service_token|mTLS service-to-service token|x-service-token

@S JournalEntry|Modernised journal entry payload
 entryId|string|required|uuid|Primary key
 postingDate|string|required|date|Effective accounting date
 accountId|string|required|uuid|GeneralLedger account ID
 amount|number|required||Posted amount in account currency
 amountBase|number|||Base-currency translation
 fxRate|number|||FX rate snapshot
 sourceKind|string|required||MANUAL|PAYMENT|CDC|FX_REVAL|RECON_ADJUSTMENT|IMPORT
 sourceEventId|string||uuid|Upstream event identifier
 postedBy|string|required||Acting principal
 postedAt|string|required|date-time|Server-side posting timestamp
 reversesEntryId|string||uuid|Reversed entry, if applicable
 batchId|string||uuid|Batch identifier
 version|integer|required||Increments on supersession

@S GeneralLedger|Modernised account payload
 accountId|string|required|uuid|Primary key
 accountCode|string|required||Chart of accounts code
 accountName|string|required||Display name
 status|string|required||ACTIVE|INACTIVE|CLOSED|FROZEN
 currency|string|required||ISO currency
 openedAt|string|required|date-time|Opening date

@S ReconciliationRun|Reconciliation run summary
 runId|string|required|uuid|Primary key
 period|string|required||YYYY-MM
 status|string|required||RUNNING|SUCCESS|VARIANCE|FAILED
 varianceTotal|number|||Total variance
 gatePassed|boolean|||Whether close was allowed

@S AuditEvent|Audit event payload
 auditId|string|required|uuid|Primary key
 eventTs|string|required|date-time|Event timestamp
 actor|string|required||Acting principal (always present in v2)
 entity|string|required||Entity name
 entityId|string|required|uuid|Entity ID
 operation|string|required||INSERT|UPDATE|SUPERSEDE|REVERSE|CLOSE|GATE

@EP GET /accounts|Lists active accounts|listAccounts
@EP POST /accounts|Creates a new account|createAccount
@EP GET /accounts/{id}|Returns a single account|getAccount
@EP PATCH /accounts/{id}|Updates an account (mutates lifecycle)|patchAccount
@EP GET /journal|Lists journal entries with filters|listJournalEntries
@EP POST /journal|Posts a new manual journal entry|createJournalEntry
@EP POST /journal/{id}/reverse|Reverses an entry|reverseJournalEntry
@EP GET /journal/{id}/audit|Returns audit trail for the entry|getJournalAuditTrail
@EP POST /reconciliation/{period}|Triggers reconciliation for a period|runReconciliation
@EP GET /reconciliation/{period}|Returns reconciliation status|getReconciliation
@EP POST /close/{period}|Triggers month-end close|runMonthEndClose
@EP GET /close/{period}/gate|Returns gate status for the close|getCloseGate
@EP GET /audit/stream|Server-sent stream of audit events|streamAudit

@R JournalEntry -> GeneralLedger|references|JournalEntry posts against an account
@R AuditEvent -> JournalEntry|references|AuditEvent often refers to a journal mutation
@R ReconciliationRun -> JournalEntry|aggregates|Reconciliation summarises journal entries
